t may not want to respond to a comment talking about what movie you just saw the other day. It's not that we don't care, it's just not a part of the game which we are trying to play. Now there may be nights where we might want to take part in that conversation and other nights where we don't. But to make a blanket statement like we are cold because of it is just unfounded.<br>
<br>
